{"tid":514211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"傻閪先會唔見電話","createTime":"2017-12-30T10:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T11:06:19.000Z","uid":151917,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58361e742a34e174b9f91ca9e2088c243496696f","tid":514211,"uid":151917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就係果個傻閪 只望好心人幫忙<br />\n細佬我今日4點幾鐘搭72號巴士 往太和方向 坐上層唔見左部iphone 6s plus 仲有個電話殼反轉cup住個mon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 電話入面有好多重要嘅資料 不過就冇電話卡係入面 我知衰架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但求有心人可以高抬貴手 幫忙俾返我<br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電話入過水唔值錢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好攞左去清除資料呀求求你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n傻閪公開決定自己tg期望有人汁到俾返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/missmyiphone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmissmyiphone&d=PANdaGv%2FftUdcD9Ayq7HxsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6c3fdcf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/missmyiphone</a>"},{"pid":"82d67e9b4d7e22116508a2ade19bc4895c7928f5","tid":514211,"uid":151917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:33:40.000Z","msg":"望各位巴絲幫忙 感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8ea0178dfa996f9c1984521ccbfe3654c7f67c","tid":514211,"uid":151917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我愛連登"},{"pid":"45a5510d7eca8d563231252aa3354df1b8644b52","tid":514211,"uid":111175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:37:5